sequenceDiagram
    participant U as Utilizador
    participant B as Browser
    participant S as TanStack Start SSR
    participant R as TanStack Router
    participant L as Layout
    participant P as Pagina
    participant D as politrace-data.ts

    U->>B: Acede a uma rota
    B->>S: Pedido HTTP
    S->>R: Resolve rota
    R->>L: Renderiza layout global
    L->>P: Renderiza outlet da pagina
    P->>D: Importa dados estaticos
    D-->>P: Arrays e tipos
    P-->>B: HTML, JS e CSS renderizados
